item.title: CVE-2023-28753|2024-08-02T13:51:37.299Z -- facebook -- netconsd
item.description: netconsd prior to v0.2 was vulnerable to an integer overflow in its parse_packet function. A malicious individual could leverage this overflow to create heap memory corruption with attacker controlled data.
